---
title: Greek Breaded Chicken With Sweet Potato Fries and Chopped Salad
description: OPA! Greek-spiced chicken, savoury roasted sweet potato fries and DIY garlic tzatziki sauce! Don't forget the tomato, cucumber and feta chopped salad to round out this weeknight winner!
